&gt;Pursuit is light for the moment as after being rebuffed, the combined airfleet of bugs and Marauders regrouped around a descending Aero-cruiser which you managed to slip out from under just in the nick of time.
&gt;Your would-be pursuers seemed unsure of how to proceed, namely who exactly to chase.
